商，就機動遊戲機的使用及操作許可證申請，惟他們尚未交齊文件，署方一直與他們聯絡及接觸，申請現正處理中。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新電視劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前好似係csl"},{"pid":"6dded21d664a5d3d79b3ca18c9bdf4f2150ba9d7","tid":454461,"uid":72306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:08:40.000Z","msg":"黑箱作業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4149b84af200d49bfe422328b5c46c1079a62b6d","tid":454461,"uid":144018,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"網上所見大部份網民都被新票價為之吸引，紛紛表示要係重開後「流連在這幸福摩天輪」<br />\n但大家仲記唔記得早前既易手風波？<br />\n<br />\n中環摩天輪易手風波事件簿<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TourisMan.hk/posts/2002725733337386:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTourisMan.hk%2Fposts%2F2002725733337386%3A0&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ef914756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TourisMan.hk/posts/2002725733337386:0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人真係好善忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd06c6dd5180793d999ad3c259ed0f8074248cb","tid":454461,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"上次果間都未有得賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9a5fe49fbcb5b273d56ff1a34ac9bd96d00515","tid":454461,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次果間都未有得賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印象中係無啦啦新果間變到錢出黎買個摩天輪？舊果間好似無乜蝕水，但新果間 d 錢就唔知邊度黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00756b75ea5fbe9272f42ef28e100049be1410d9","tid":454461,"uid":68672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"